message.body: Hi, how are you today?
Hi. Okay.still waking up. I got off work on fri. That's when you're doing bday stuff, right?
Nate is organizing something on Saturday but I don't know much about it, but I am also free on Saturday
I mean Friday
Hmmm. Okay. Do you have Ella on Friday?
No, I won't have Ella on Friday

I make a really good one. Do you want to do something special on Friday? Or should I try to get off on Saturday?
I would love to see you Friday if you work on Saturday. Saturday was the night Nate was organizing something, but I don't know much about it
Cool.

Sorry. Hang Friday!
